If you have lost your car engine, visit Directorate of Criminal Investigations offices in Juja, Kiambu county. DCI Special Service Unit officers have recovered five suspected stolen motor vehicle engines at Rurii market in Juja Sub county. "We were acting on a tip off from members of the public, Those who may have lost their engines are advised to visit Juja police station," DCI George Kinoti said. Kinoti said investigations are ongoing as pursuit for the suspects intensifies.